Package: roslyngr
Type: Package
Title: Motion Charts Using Plotly and Shiny for Data Exploration
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Dan", "Smilowitz", email = "dan.smilowitz@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides multiple graphical representations of datasets using
    Plotly in a Shiny app.  Recreates the Hans-Rosling-style "motion" chart
    along with additional single- and multiple-variable visualization options.
    Allows for customization of visualization variables (axes, colors, size) to
    provide a smoother version of the googleVis motion chart.
Imports:
    plotly,
    shiny,
    tidyverse
Suggests:
    gapminder
URL: https://github.com/dsmilo/roslyngr
License: MIT | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true